==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī bù cùo, bù bù cùo

===Phrase===
'''[[一]][[步]][[错]]，[[步]][[步]][[错]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# If the ones in front make a misstep, then all the ones following will likewise make a misstep.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[步]][[錯]]，[[步]][[步]][[錯]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

